 style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">. </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">With the support of these agencies SACH has </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">created</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">joint activities </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">between Israeli</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">s a</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">nd </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">Palestinian</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">s from a grassroots level</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> (providing cardiac care to children and training to doctors)</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> into </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">a</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt">n institutionalized</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> framework</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> that ensures</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> that</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> Palestinian children suffering from rheumatic and congenital heart disease can receive treatment from</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11.5pt"> local physicians within their community. </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">THOUGHTS</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">AND</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">RECOMMENDATIONS</span></p><ol start="11" type="1" styl